y once downloaded. Link for downloading can be found in the e-mail message with firmware image archive download link. Please be noted, that mass-production content may differ from a customized (B2B) projects content.</li>\r\n\t<li>Reset device to factory defaults using &#39;Settings&#39; menu of the device.</li>\r\n</ol>	2017-12-11 14:35:14.551734+00	2017-12-12 10:22:20.970355+00	3
