ge. Please double check the &lsquo;spam&rsquo; or &lsquo;junk&rsquo; folders if no e-mail received.</li>\r\n\t<li>Unzip the archive and burn the appeared firmware image to the known good micro SD card with&nbsp;<strong>Etcher&nbsp;</strong>program.</li>\r\n\t<li>Insert micro SD card with the burned image into the device card reader and turn on the device by&nbsp;pressing &lsquo;power on button&rsquo; for 1 sec.</li>\r\n\t<li>Following the instructions on display, make primary device settings.</li>\r\n\t<li>Power on the device and connect it via USB cable to your PC.</li>\r\n\t<li>Provide additional diagnostic procedures if needed (touch screen, Wi-Fi, etc.)</li>\r\n\t<li>Copy &lsquo;Content&rsquo; folders to the root catalog of the internal microSD card of the device. Content is the&nbsp;same for all devices of this model and can be used constantly once downloaded. Link for downloading&nbsp;can be found in the e-mail message with firmware image archive download link. Please be noted, that&nbsp;mass-production content may differ from a customized (B2B) projects content.</li>\r\n\t<li>Reset device to factory defaults using internal Settings menu of the device.</li>\r\n</ol>	2017-12-11 15:38:29.208845+00	2018-05-07 11:00:15.110794+00	15
