 e-mail box (selected in previous point)&nbsp;and download image archive, using link from the received message. Please double check the &lsquo;spam&rsquo; or &lsquo;junk&rsquo; folders if no e-mail received.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>Unzip the archive and copy the appeared SWUPDATE.BIN file to the root catalog of internal memory of the device.</li>\r\n\t<li>Press &#39;Forward&#39; button on the turned on device for start&nbsp;firmware proces.<img alt="" src="/media/uploads/2018/04/20/3.png" style="height:228px; width:645px" /></li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Following the instructions on display, make primary device settings.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Provide additional diagnostic procedures if needed (touch screen, Wi-Fi, etc.)</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Copy &lsquo;Content&rsquo; folders to the root catalog of the internal microSD card of the device. Content is the same for all devices of this model and can be used constantly once downloaded. Link for downloading can be found in the e-mail message with firmware image archive download link. Please be noted, that mass-production content may differ from a customized (B2B) projects content.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t<p>Reset device to factory defaults using internal Settings menu of the device.</p>\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	2018-06-06 11:31:36.293518+00	2018-06-06 13:16:07.861342+00	19
